javax.wsdl
Interface Operation

All Superinterfaces:
AttributeExtensible, ElementExtensible, java.io.Serializable, WSDLElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
OperationImpl
public interface Operation
extends WSDLElement

This interface represents a WSDL operation. It includes information on input, output and fault messages associated with usage of the operation.

Author:
Paul Fremantle (pzf@us.ibm.com), Nirmal Mukhi (nmukhi@us.ibm.com), Matthew J. Duftler (duftler@us.ibm.com)
